name: M Haidar Hanif
title: Founder, Engineer, Mentor
bio: Haidar is the founder of Catamyst. A lifelong learner, engineer, and educator. Actively mentoring people to help them transition into tech careers or upgrading their skills. Previously had several years experience of teaching, training, and building a coding school.

name: Maya Asmara
title: Co-Founder, Writer, Mentor
bio: Maya is the co-founder of Catamyst. An avid writer and content creator. Consistently spreading messages about the importance of happiness in work and life.

name: Latifah Dhia
title: Illustrator
bio: Latifah is the illustrator of Catamyst. Currently drawing interesting visuals on this platform.
